Entry.JapaneseText: オレらはずっと 思ってたんだ
ダオスがもっと、 しっかりしていれば、 戦争は起きなかったって
Entry.EnglishText: Had you ruled in a different way, the war would have never happened.

Entry.JapaneseText: 筋違いってわかってた。 でも、わたしたちは勝手に あなたを恨みに思ってました
Entry.EnglishText: I know it sounds absurd...But we held deep resentment towards you.

Entry.JapaneseText: そんなわたしたちの想いを あなたはひとりで背負い 苦悩してたんですね
Entry.EnglishText: But we didn't know you had to bear so many painful things on your own...

Entry.JapaneseText: もはや葛藤など捨てた
今のあなたの存在、それが 葛藤の徴（しるし）……
Entry.EnglishText: Your existence right now...it embodies grieving...

Entry.JapaneseText: その葛藤があなたの 優しさの証……
Entry.EnglishText: And that mourning is a sign of your kindness...

Entry.JapaneseText: ……オレらもちゃんと 自分の罪に向き合う
Entry.EnglishText: ...We need to face against our sins, too.

Entry.JapaneseText: あんたが不安に向き合って、 戦い続けたのと同じで
Entry.EnglishText: You had to keep on fighting despite your contradictory feelings.

Entry.JapaneseText: オレらもちゃんと決着をつける
Entry.EnglishText: We need to set things right.

Entry.JapaneseText: ……私はおまえたちの行ったことを 取り返せるとは思わぬ
Entry.EnglishText: ... I did not expect you to genuinely try to undo your wrongs.

Entry.JapaneseText: 我が星、デリス・カーラーンは 滅びの危機を迎えた
Entry.EnglishText: I was faced to accept my dear home planet, Derris Kharlan, was to be fully destroyed.

Entry.JapaneseText: そして私自身は、自分の怒り、 憎しみ、慢心……自分の心に 敗北し息絶えたのだ
Entry.EnglishText: And then inside of me a myriad of strong emotions welled up... Shock, sadness, anger... At that time my heart died.

Entry.JapaneseText: この世に悪と呼べるものが あるとすれば、それは人の心だ
Entry.EnglishText: If there is evil in this world, it lurks in the hearts of men.

Entry.JapaneseText: そして、最も恐るべきもの。 勝たねばならない敵…… それが自分の心だ
Entry.EnglishText: That is a dreadful truth. My heart...it became an undefeatable enemy.

Entry.JapaneseText: おまえたちは、 自分から分かれた自分の心と 向き合っている
Entry.EnglishText: You have come here on your own accord to face my lingering feelings.

Entry.JapaneseText: 決着をつけるがよい。 おまえたちの大罪の始末を
Entry.EnglishText: So you want to make the wrongs right. You will acknowledge and clean your sin...

Entry.JapaneseText: 戻ろうぜ、 オレらの時代に
Entry.EnglishText: Let's go back to our time.

Entry.JapaneseText: ディオスとメルティアは <Red>審理の晶谷<White>にいるよ
Entry.EnglishText: <DIO>s and <MEL>tia are at the Crystal Trial Valley.

Entry.JapaneseText: 君たちの罪の行方 見守るって言ったでしょ
Entry.EnglishText: I did say I'd look after your sin until the end, didn't I?

Entry.JapaneseText: 私の知りたかった 色んなこと……
Entry.EnglishText: All of the things I wanted to know...

Entry.JapaneseText: 双子ちゃんのおかげで 知ることができたから
Entry.EnglishText: Thanks to you twins I could learn all about it.
